USA: 153 runs in 40.5 overs (246 balls, 168 mins)

PNG: 50 runs in 16.3 overs (99 balls, 80 mins)
PNG: 100 runs in 25.1 overs(151 balls, 115 mins)

milestones.description: Steven Taylor and Monank Patel's 5-run partnership is USA's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 1 between Leon Romero and Alexander
Hayden Walsh and Monank Patel's 43-run partnership is USA's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 8 between Lambert and Alexander
Timil Patel and Netravalkar's 39-run partnership is USA's highest for the 9th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 10 between Tony Reid and Rashid
Timil Patel and Ali Khan's 16-run partnership is USA's highest for the 10th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 12 between Nasir Javed and Johnson
Timil Patel has become the top scorer for USA in ODIs with 50 runs, going past Lambert's 39
Timil Patel's 50 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for USA), surpassing Lambert's 39
Timil Patel has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (28) in an innings in ODIs for USA, going past Lambert's 22
Assad Vala has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (19) for PNG, going past Mahuru Dai
Malhotra has broken the record for most dismissals in an innings (2) in ODIs for USA, going past Mark Johnson's 1
Lega Siaka has scored 1 hundreds in ODIs, the most for PNG breaking Tony Ura's record
